== Yoland Makolo ==
kuwa 30 Nyakanga 2021nibwo ibiro bya [[Ministry of Infrastructure (Rwanda) - MININFRA|Minisitiri]] wintebe byatangaje k Yoland Makolo

yagizwe umuvugizi wa [[Geworugiya|Guverinoma]] muri minisiteri yububanyi namahanga nubutwererane<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/yolande-makolo-yagizwe-umuvugizi-wa-guverinoma-muri-minisiteri-y-ububanyi-n-amahanga</ref>

== Amateka ==
Yoland Makolo yavukiye muri [[kongo]] papa we umubyara akaba ari umu kongoman wo mubwoko

bwa Luba mugace bita [[Congo Brazzaville|Kassai]] na Nyina wu umunyarwandakazi<ref>https://www.kapitalafrik.com/2021/08/02/rwanda-yolande-makolo-appointed-government-spokesperson/</ref>

